</ul>
<p>To get this extension, you can contact us directly with the&nbsp;<a href="http://www.wascou.org/Contact-us" target="_self">contact form</a>.</p><a name="eztoc8666_2" id="eztoc8666_2"></a><h2>What is the next step ?</h2><p>The next step is to choose next features to implement amid this ones :</p>
<ul>

<li>#49: Add a list system</li>

<li>#50: Add a system to shorten URL</li>

<li>#73: Add a moderation system</li>

</ul>
<p>If you have other ideas, let us know, we will add it to the list.</p><p>Let a comment to this post so we can know what is the most important.</p>
